{"prompt": "Generate a website for a local artist portfolio. The website should be professional and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Artist Portfolio</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #e52b50; /* Red brand color */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid #c11b44;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        #about, #portfolio, #contact {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #about img {\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 200px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 5px solid #e52b50;\n        }\n        #portfolio .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        #portfolio .gallery img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        #portfolio .gallery img:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.05);\n        }\n        #contact form {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            display: inline-block;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 300px;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        #contact button {\n            display: block;\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            background-color: #e52b50;\n            color: #fff;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: #c11b44;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>[Artist Name]</h1>\n            <p>Exploring the World Through [Art Style]</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Me</h2>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200\" alt=\"Artist Photo\">\n            <p>Welcome to my portfolio! I am a passionate artist specializing in [briefly describe your art and style]. My work is often inspired by [mention inspirations]. I strive to evoke [emotions or feelings] through my creations.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"portfolio\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>My Work</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200\" alt=\"Artwork 1\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200\" alt=\"Artwork 2\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200\" alt=\"Artwork 3\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200\" alt=\"Artwork 4\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200\" alt=\"Artwork 5\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200\" alt=\"Artwork 6\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Interested in a commission or have a question? Feel free to reach out!</p>\n            <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" rows=\"4\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 [Artist Name]. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            const name = document.getElementById('name').value;\n            const email = document.getElementById('email').value;\n            const message = document.getElementById('message').value;\n\n            // In a real application, you would send this data to a server.\n            // For this example, we'll just log it to the console.\n            console.log('Form submitted:');\n            console.log('Name:', name);\n            console.log('Email:', email);\n            console.log('Message:', message);\n\n            alert('Thank you for your message! I will be in touch soon.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}